{"type": "article", "id": 25680, "title": "英特尔可能要进 iPhone 7 了", "description": "iPhone, Intel Inside", "date": "2016-04-19T14:55:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 15634, "name": "iPhone 7"}, {"id": 3245, "name": "芯片"}, {"id": 1014, "name": "英特尔"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 2920, "name": "高通"}], "category": 4, "author": 3910, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607101212sQDO2hFiw3rcn0eG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">iPhone 要用英特尔处理器了，但不是 CPU。</p>\n<p>“高通依然为主要供应商，但英特尔很可能从苹果手里拿到 3000 万到 4000 万颗芯片组订单。”投资银行 Canaccord Genuity <wbr><a href=\"http://www.investors.com/news/technology/intel-expected-to-swipe-30-40-mil-apple-iphone-7s-from-qualcomm/\">分析师 </a><a href=\"http://www.investors.com/news/technology/intel-expected-to-swipe-30-40-mil-apple-iphone-7s-from-qualcomm/\">Mike Walkley 在最近的报告中写道</a>。<br></wbr></p>\n<p class=\"\">这里的芯片不是英特尔成名的 CPU，而是用来传输移动网络的通信芯片（也叫基带）。</p>\n<p>市场咨询公司 BlueFin Research Partners 的<a href=\"http://fortune.com/2016/04/18/intel-iphone-7-chip-business/\">分析师 </a><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2016/04/18/intel-iphone-7-chip-business/\">Steve Mullane 认为</a>，英特尔塞进 iPhone 7 的将是 7360 通信芯片。</p>\n<p>此前高通包揽了 iPhone 的通信芯片。不过根据 Mullane 的分析，此次英特尔拿到的仅仅是 30% 甚至更少。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">但介于苹果每年生产一亿多部 iPhone，30% 依然是一个庞大的数量。也是英特尔急需的订单。</p>\n<p>仅 2014 年，英特尔在移动芯片领域就亏损了 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=5&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjopL6O85nMAhXIKJQKHcFNDK4QFgg6MAQ&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2015-01-16%2Fintel-s-4-21-billion-mobile-loss-would-have-sunk-most-rivals&amp;usg=AFQjCNEjRbwDtpDqE-bgBqmGXeqiZvCE-Q&amp;sig2=pC0PZC0Zn4OAWjvfP1BvSA&amp;bvm=bv.119745492,d.dGo\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">40 亿美元</a>。2015 年财报结构调整，移动芯片并入 PC 业务，你都不知道英特尔去年亏了多少。但你能看到移动芯片部门的负责人<a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/intel-mobile-chip-chief-to-depart-1459557840\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </a><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/intel-mobile-chip-chief-to-depart-1459557840\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Aicha Evans </a><a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/intel-mobile-chip-chief-to-depart-1459557840\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">离职</a>。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">苹果选择多家供应商的理由不难理解，如果生产中出现任何问题，能够及时调整。此前 iPhone 6s 所用的 A9 处理器分别交给三星和台积电生产。而 iPhone 的存储器、屏幕也都是分给多家产生的结果。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj5vPG48pnMAhWGspQKHfObB98QjhwIBQ&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theoverclocker.com%2Fnew-intel-ceo-president-outline-product-plans-future-of-computing-vision-to-mobilize-intel-and-developers%2F&amp;psig=AFQjCNEc9byJuj8Z4f9tGWdcwy1eqxiWvQ&amp;ust=1461127551962298\">Theoverclocker</a></p>\n\n\n"}